                  </persName>
            . I was with my brother and saw him find the timber.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>The prisoner put in a written Defence, stating that he had used the wood in his work, and thought it belonged to the Company.</p>
               <p>GEORGE THOMAS re-examined. The distance between the two wharfs is only the width of the gate; when I spoke to the prisoner, he said "Say nothing about it; if you do, I shall lose my birth and get out of bread."</p>
